$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
random_al

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
random_al -  This method returns a random alignment between the limits for the given deity.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int random_al(string deity)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^deity%^RESET%^ - the name of the deity
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
a random valid alignment

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/deity_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns a random alignment between the limits for the
given deity.  This is used by NPCs to set themselves up
with a correct alignment for their deity.
.EP

